Introduction

POA (Korean: 피오에이) or Project on Air (Korean: 프로젝트 온에어) was a South Korean girl group under HANDMADE and KMG (Korea Music Group) consisting of five members: Yubeen, Ria, Jihyun, Songjour and Dana. They made their debut on September 21, 2022 with "On Air Stand Up". They silently disbanded sometime in early 2023.
